==细胞质不兼容==
[[Image:Uni bidirectional ci.png|thumb|right|500px|'''Unidirectional CI:''' 被感染的雄性与未被感染的雌性导致了受精卵的CI。<br />
'''Bidirectional CI:''' 感染菌株I的雄性与感染菌株II的雌性导致了受精卵的CI。]]
细胞质不兼容（Cytoplasmic incompatibility，CI）是沃尔巴克氏体造成的一种生殖现象：被感染的雄性与未被感染的雌性或者感染了不同菌株的雌性交配产下的受精卵不能发育而死亡。换句话说，被感染的雌性能兼容未被感染的雄性或者感染了同样菌株的雄性。<ref name="Werren" />宿主通过抗生素治疗可以从沃尔巴克氏体感染中治愈。

在[[二倍体|二倍体]]生物中，CI导致了胚胎死亡。而在[[单倍体|单倍体]]宿主中，CI导致了单倍体的雄性后代。<ref>Tram, U, Fredrick, K, Werren, J, Sullivan, W (2006). "Paternal chromosome segregation during the first mitotic division determines ''Wolbachia''-induced cytoplasmic incompatibility phenotype", ''J. Cell Sci.'' 119, 10.1242/jcs.03095. http://jcs.biologists.org/cgi/content/abstract/119/17/3655 {{Wayback|url=http://jcs.biologists.org/cgi/content/abstract/119/17/3655 |date=20100818002217 }}</ref>

=== 细胞机制 ===
细胞质不兼容可归因到2个不同的事件。第一个发生在感染了沃尔巴克氏体的雄性的[[精子发生|精子发生]]阶段被称作修改（modification）。因为沃尔巴克氏体不存在于成熟的精子中，因此沃尔巴克氏体必定修改了感染的雄性的精子发生。<ref>Snook, R, Cleland, S, Wolfner, M, Karr T (2000). "Offsetting Effects of Wolbachia Infection and Heat Shock on Sperm Production in Drosophila simulans: Analyses of Fecundity, Fertility and Accessory Gland Proteins", ''Genetics'' 155: 167-178. http://www.genetics.org/cgi/content/full/155/1/167 {{Wayback|url=http://www.genetics.org/cgi/content/full/155/1/167 |date=20090319154540 }}</ref>第二个事件，稱
为营救（rescue），发生于受精卵中的沃尔巴克氏体阻止了CI发生。只要卵中的沃尔巴克氏体菌株与精子发生时的菌株对应，受精卵中就不会发生CI。

CI的主要后果是在雄性的[[原核|原核]]的有丝分裂被延迟；第二个后果是这种不同时性导致父本染色体在有丝分裂第一阶段的赤道板上不能正常凝聚并对齐。只有母本染色体分离正常产生单倍体胚胎。<ref name="Tram" />受精卵中CI的营救导致了父本与母本的原核恢复同步。<ref name="Tram">{{cite journal | last1 = Tram | first1 = U | last2 = Sullivan | first2 = W | year = 2002 | title = Role of delayed nuclear envelope breakdown and mitosis in Wolbachia-induced cytoplasmic incompability | url = http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/abstract/296/5570/1124 | journal = Science | volume = 296 | issue =  | pages = 1124–1126 | doi = 10.1126/science.1070536 | access-date = 2015-06-12 | archive-date = 2010-08-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100816155910/http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/abstract/296/5570/1124 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Lassy | first1 = C | last2 = Karr | first2 = T | year = 1996 | title = Cytological analysis of fertilization and early embryonic development in incompatible crosses of Drosophila simulans | url = http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/B6T9H-3VYTMKV-4/2/b22cf619a1a4f955659c763db4619218 | journal = Mechanisms of Development | volume = 57 | issue = 1| pages = 47–58 | doi=10.1016/0925-4773(96)00527-8}}</ref>

沃尔巴克氏体如何导致修改与营救，仍然未知。果蝇的早期感染导致了精子{{tsl|en|chromatin remodeling|染色质重塑}}阶段可以观察到CI。<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Landmann | first1 = F | last2 = Orsi | first2 = GA | last3 = Loppin | first3 = B | last4 = Sullivan | first4 = W | year = 2009 | title = Wolbachia-Mediated Cytoplasmic Incompatibility Is Associated with Impaired Histone Deposition in the Male Pronucleus | url = | journal = PLoS Pathog | volume = 5 | issue = 3| page = e1000343 | doi = 10.1371/journal.ppat.1000343 }}</ref>然而其他一些宿主物种的CI只出现于受精卵发育阶段。<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Duron | first1 = O | last2 = Weill | first2 = M | year = 2006 | title = Wolbachia infection influences the development of Culex pipiens embryo in incompatible crosses | url =https://archive.org/details/sim_heredity_2006-06_96_6/page/n78| journal = Heredity | volume = 96 | issue = 6| pages = 493–500 | doi = 10.1038/sj.hdy.6800831 }}</ref>

===演化影响===
Werren<ref name="Werren">{{cite journal | last1 = Werren | first1 = J | year = 1997 | title = Biology of Wolbachia | url = http://www.rochester.edu/college/bio/labs/WerrenLab/My%20Papers/1997_Wolbach_AnRevEnt.pdf | format = PDF | journal = Annual Review of Entomology | volume = 42 | issue =  | pages = 587–609 | doi = 10.1146/annurev.ento.42.1.587 | access-date = 2015-06-12 | archive-date = 2020-10-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201031064349/http://www.rochester.edu/College/BIO/labs/WerrenLab/My%20Papers/1997_Wolbach_AnRevEnt.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>指出沃尔巴克氏体导致了对未感染的雌性宿主的选择压力，因为感染的雌性可以与已感染或未感染的雄性交配繁衍后代，但未感染的雌性只能与未感染的雄性交配生殖。由于沃尔巴克氏体只能由雌性传播给子代，这种机制促进了沃尔巴克氏体的扩散。 群体遗传学中，沃尔巴克氏体感染率超过10%会使得感染的个体在代际传播上取得优势地位。<ref name="Fine">{{cite journal | last1 = Fine | first1 = P | year = 1978 | title = On the Dynamics of Symbiote-Dependent Cytoplasmic Incompatibility in Culicine Mosquitoes | url = | journal = J Invertebr Pathol | volume = 30 | issue = | pages = 10–18 }}</ref>and Stouthamer et al. 
<ref name="Stouthamer">{{cite journal | last1 = Stouthamer | first1 = R | year = 1999 | title = WOLBACHIA PIPIENTIS: Microbial Manipulator of Arthropod Reproduction | url =https://archive.org/details/sim_annual-review-of-microbiology_1999_53/page/71| journal = Annual Review of Microbiology | volume = 53 | issue = | pages = 71–102 | doi = 10.1146/annurev.micro.53.1.71 }}</ref>这位成为入侵阈值。

如果同一物种的两个群体分别感染了沃尔巴克氏体的两个不同的菌株，由于CI这会导致这个宿主群体的生殖隔离。两个群体的这种基因的分离会导致物种的分化。

==沃尔巴克氏体感染造成的适应优势 ==
沃尔巴克氏体已被证实有助于[[黑腹果蝇|黑腹果蝇]]与蚊子的抗病毒。感染了沃尔巴克氏体的蝇更抗RNA病毒如{{tsl|en|Drosophila C virus|果蝇C病毒}}、[[诺沃克病毒|诺沃克病毒]]、{{tsl|en|Flock house virus|羊舍病毒}}、{{tsl|en|Cricket paralysis virus|蟋蟀麻痹病毒}}, [[基孔肯雅熱|基孔肯雅熱]]病毒、[[西尼罗河病毒|西尼罗河病毒]]。<ref>{{Cite journal |first1=Luis |last1=Teixeira |first2=Alvaro|last2=Ferreira |first3=Michael |last3=Ashburner |title=The Bacterial Symbiont Wolbachia Induces Resistance to RNA Viral Infections in ''Drosophila melanogaster'' |journal=[[PLOS_Biology|PLOS Biology]] |volume=6 |issue=12 | pmid=19222304| doi=10.1371/journal.pbio.1000002 |pmc=2605931 |year=2008 |editor1-last=Keller |editor1-first=Laurent |pages=e2}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal |first1=Lauren |last1=Hedges |first2=Jeremy|last2=Brownlie |first3=Scott |last3=O'Neill | first4=Karyn| last4=Johnson| title=Wolbachia and Virus Protection in  Insects |journal=[[Science_(journal)|Science]] |volume=322 | doi = 10.1126/science.1162418 |year=2008 |issue=5902 |pages=702  |bibcode = 2008Sci...322..702H }}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal |first1=Robert L. |last1=Glaser |first2=Mark A. |last2=Meola |title=The Native Wolbachia Endosymbionts of ''Drosophila melanogaster'' and ''Culex quinquefasciatus'' Increase Host Resistance to West Nile Virus Infection|journal=PLOS Biology |volume=5 |issue=6 |pmid=20700535 | doi = 10.1371/journal.pone.0011977 |year=2010 |editor1-last=Liu |editor1-first=Ding Xiang |pages=e11977 |pmc=2916829|bibcode = 2010PLoSO...511977G }}</ref>对于常见的室内蚊子，沃尔巴克氏体感染率高相关于更高的杀虫剂抵抗。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Berticat C, Rousset F, Raymond M, Berthomieu A, Weill M |title=High Wolbachia density in insecticide-resistant mosquitoes |journal=Proc. Biol. Sci. |volume=269 |issue=1498 |pages=1413–6 |date=July 2002 |pmid=12079666 |pmc=1691032 |doi=10.1098/rspb.2002.2022 |url=http://rspb.royalsocietypublishing.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=12079666}}</ref>一种[[潜叶虫|潜叶虫]]——{{tsl|en|Phyllonorycter blancardella|斑幕潜叶蛾}}，在秋天植物葉子枯黃时仍然能保持该潛葉蟲附近的區域的叶子仍然保持鮮綠，繼續進行光合作用，使得潜叶虫可以继续进食、生长。如果对该潜叶虫施加[[四环霉素|四环霉素]]，杀死其体内的沃尔巴克氏体，则失去了在枯黄植株上保持“绿道”能力，随之仅13%的该潜叶虫能羽化成蛾。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Kaiser W, Huguet E, Casas J, Commin C, Giron D |title=Plant green-island phenotype induced by leaf-miners is mediated by bacterial symbionts |journal=Proc. Biol. Sci. |volume=277 |issue=1692 |pages=2311–9 |date=August 2010 |pmid=20356892 |pmc=2894905 |doi=10.1098/rspb.2010.0214 |url=http://rspb.royalsocietypublishing.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=20356892}}</ref>被潛葉蟲寄生的[[樺樹|樺樹]]的“绿岛”有大量[[細胞分裂素|細胞分裂素]]（cytokinins），但研究並未指出該細胞分裂素是由沃尔巴克氏体自行合成，或者沃尔巴克氏体刺激植物合成或者。沃尔巴克氏体可能帶有一些也能在植物體內找到的基因。這些基因能合成細胞分裂素，來喚醒植物細胞或延遲凋亡。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.sciencemag.org/plants-animals/2010/07/bacteria-bring-leaves-back-dead |title=Bacteria Bring Leaves Back From the Dead, By Daniel Strain, 23 July 2010  |access-date=2015-06-12 |archive-date=2014-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140818022638/http://news.sciencemag.org/plants-animals/2010/07/bacteria-bring-leaves-back-dead |dead-url=no }}</ref>

沃尔巴克氏体能够刺激被感染的{{tsl|en|Drosophila simulans|拟果蝇}}产卵能力显著增强。<ref>{{Cite journal |first1=A.R. |last1=Weeks |first2=M.|last2=Turelli |first3=W.R. |last3=Harcombe |title=From parasite to mutualist: rapid evolution of ''Wolbachia'' in natural populations of ''Drosophila'' |journal=[[PLOS_Biology|PLOS Biology]] |volume=5 |issue=5 | doi=10.1371/journal.pbio.0050114 |year=2007 }}</ref>

属于[[线虫动物门|线虫动物门]]的{{tsl|en|Brugia malayi|马来丝虫}}， 沃尔巴克氏体是必需的内共生菌，提供给宿主必需的化学物。<ref>{{Cite journal |first1=Jeremy |last1=Foster|first2=Mehul |last2=Ganatra| first3= et al. |title=The Wolbachia Genome of Brugia malayi: Endosymbiont Evolution within a Human Pathogenic Nematode|journal=[[PLos_Biology|PLos Biology]] |volume=3 |issue=4 |pmid=15780005 |year=2005 |pages=e121 |doi=10.1371/journal.pbio.0030121 |pmc=1069646 |last3=Kamal |last4=Ware |first4=Jennifer |last5=Makarova |first5=Kira |last6=Ivanova |first6=Natalia |last7=Bhattacharyya |first7=Anamitra |last8=Kapatral |first8=Vinayak |last9=Kumar |first9=Sanjay|last10=Posfai|first10=Janos|last11=Vincze|first11=Tamas|last12=Ingram|first12=Jessica|last13=Moran|first13=Laurie|last14=Lapidus|first14=Alla|last15=Omelchenko|first15=Marina|last16=Kyrpides|first16=Nikos|last17=Ghedin|first17=Elodie|last18=Wang|first18=Shiliang|last19=Goltsman|first19=Eugene|last20=Joukov|first20=Victor|last21=Ostrovskaya|first21=Olga|last22=Tsukerman|first22=Kiryl|last23=Mazur|first23=Mikhail|last24=Comb|first24=Donald|last25=Koonin|first25=Eugene|last26=Slatko|first26=Barton|display-authors=8}}</ref>一些节肢动物体内寄生的沃尔巴克氏体给宿主提供了某些新陈代谢必需物。黑腹果蝇在营养压力下，体内寄生的沃尔巴克氏体参与调节铁代谢。<ref>{{Cite journal |first1=J.C. |last1=Brownlie |first2=B. N.|last2=Cass |first3=M. |last3=Riegler |title=Evidence for metabolic provisioning by a common invertebrate endosymbiont, ''Wolbachia pipientis'', during periods of nutritional stress |journal=[[Plos_Pathogens|Plos Pathogens]] |volume=5 |issue=4 | doi=10.1371/journal.ppat.1000368 |year=2009 }}</ref>[[温带臭虫|温带臭虫]]体内的沃尔巴克氏体帮助宿主合成[[维生素B|维生素B]]。<ref>{{Cite journal |first1=N. |last1=Nikoh |first2=T.|last2=Hosokawa |first3=M. |last3=Moriyama |title=Evolutionary origin of insect- ''Wolbachia'' nutritional mutualism |journal=[[Proceedings_of_the_National_Academy_of_Sciences_of_the_United_States_of_America|Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the United States of America]] |volume=111 |issue=28 | doi=10.1073/pnas.1409284111 |year=2014 }}</ref>

==水平基因转移与基因组学==
沃尔巴克氏体的第一次基因组测序是对感染[[黑腹果蝇|黑腹果蝇]]的菌株。<ref name="pmid15024419">{{cite journal |author=Wu M, Sun LV, Vamathevan J, et al. |title=Phylogenomics of the Reproductive Parasite Wolbachia pipientis wMel: A Streamlined Genome Overrun by Mobile Genetic Elements |journal=PLOS Biology |volume=2 |issue=3 |pages=e69 |year=2004 |pmid=15024419 |pmc=368164 |doi=10.1371/journal.pbio.0020069 }}</ref>由{{le|約翰·克萊格·凡特研究所|J. Craig Venter Institute|基因研究所}}的{{le|喬納森·艾森|Jonathan Eisen}}与史考特·歐尼爾（{{lang|en|Scott O'Neill}}）合作完成。第二例沃尔巴克氏体测序是对感染{{tsl|en|Brugia malayi|马来丝虫}}的菌株。<ref name="pmid15780005">{{cite journal |author=Foster J, Ganatra M, Kamal I, et al. |title=The Wolbachia Genome of Brugia malayi: Endosymbiont Evolution within a Human Pathogenic Nematode |journal=PLOS Biology |volume=3 |issue=4 |pages=e121 |year=2005 |pmid=15780005 |pmc=1069646 |doi=10.1371/journal.pbio.0030121 }}</ref>{{tsl|en|Drosophila ananassae|嗜凤梨果蝇}}内寄生的沃尔巴克氏体的基因测序接近完成，其大的基因片段在其它7种果蝇体内均有发现。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Widespread Lateral Gene Transfer from Intracellular Bacteria to Multicellular Eukaryotes |author=Dunning Hotopp, J.C, Clark ME, Oliveira DC, Foster JM, Fischer P, Torres MC, Giebel JD, Kumar N, Ishmael N, Wang S, Ingram J, Nene RV, Shepard J, Tomkins J, Richards S, Spiro DJ, Ghedin E, Slatko BE, Tettelin H, Werren J.H. |journal=Science |volume=317 |issue=5845 |pages=1753–6 |year=2007 |doi=10.1126/science.1142490 |pmid=17761848|bibcode = 2007Sci...317.1753H |last2=Clark |last3=Oliveira |last4=Foster |last5=Fischer |last6=Torres |last7=Giebel |last8=Kumar |last9=Ishmael |last10=Wang |last11=Ingram |last12=Nene |last13=Shepard |last14=Tomkins |last15=Richards |last16=Spiro |last17=Ghedin |last18=Slatko |last19=Tettelin |last20=Werren }}</ref>

日本产业技术综合研究所的深津武马和[[东京大学|东京大学]]的今藤夏子，在研究农业害虫[[绿豆象|绿豆象]]和昆虫寄生细菌沃尔巴克氏体的关系时发现，沃尔巴克氏体的基因存在于绿豆象的染色体中，而且沃尔巴克氏体的染色体结构没有遭到破坏，也就是说，它的基因可以通过绿豆象这一更高级的动物遗传下去。

在一项辨识{{tsl|en|Protocalliphora|原丽蝇属}}物种的[[DNA条形码|DNA条形码]]项目中，发现几个不同的形态种（morphospecies）具有相同的线粒体细胞色素C氧化酶亚基I基因序列，可能是沃尔巴克氏体在这几个物种之间感染传播造成的[[基因水平转移|基因水平转移]]。<ref name = "Whitworthetal">{{Cite journal |last1=Whitworth |first1=TL |last2=Dawson |first2=RD |last3=Magalon |first3=H |last4=Baudry |first4=E |year=2007 |title=DNA barcoding cannot reliably identify species of the blowfly genus Protocalliphora (Diptera: Calliphoridae) |journal=[[Proceedings_of_the_Royal_Society_B|Proceedings of the Royal Society B]] |volume=274 |pmid=17472911 |issue=1619 |pages=1731–9 |doi=10.1098/rspb.2007.0062 |pmc=2493573}}</ref>这会造成错误的[[分子系统发生学|分子系统发生学]]推断的[[支序分类学|支序分类]]结果。<ref>{{Cite journal |last1=Johnstone |first1=RA |last2=Hurst |first2=GDD |year=1996 |title=Maternally inherited male-killing microorganisms may confound interpretation of mitochondrial DNA variability |journal=[[Biological_Journal_of_the_Linnean_Society|Biological Journal of the Linnean Society]] |volume=58 |issue=4 |pages=453–470 |doi=10.1111/j.1095-8312.1996.tb01446.x}}</ref>

沃尔巴克氏体内也寄生了一种温和的[[噬菌体|噬菌体]]称作WO。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Masui S, Kamoda S, Sasaki T, Ishikawa H |year=2000 |title=Distribution and evolution of bacteriophage WO in Wolbachia, the endosymbiont causing sexual alterations in arthropods. |journal=J Mol Evol |volume=5 |issue=51 |pages=491–491 |doi=10.1007/s002390010112 |pmid=11080372 |pmc= 2862486 }}</ref>比较{{tsl|en|bacteriophage WO|噬菌体WO}}基因序列提供了一些显著的在沃尔巴克氏体宿主之间大规模[[基因水平迁移|基因水平迁移]]的例子。<ref>{{Cite journal |first1=Bethany N. |last1=Kent |first2=Leonidas |last2=Salichos |first3=John G. |last3=Gibbons |first4=Antonis |last4=Rokas |first5=Irene L.| last5=Newton |first6=Michael E. |last6=Clark |first7=Seth R.|last7=Bordenstein |year=2011 |title=Complete Bacteriophage Transfer in a Bacterial Endosymbiont (Wolbachia) Determined by Targeted Genome Capture |journal=Genome in Biology and Evolution |volume=3 |pages=209–218 |doi=10.1093/gbe/evr007 |pmid=21292630 |pmc=3068000 }}</ref>这是第一个噬菌体造成的被寄生细菌的基因频繁的水平迁移的例子。这可能会大大加快细菌的细胞间基因演化过程，过去典型认为细菌基因高度稳定甚至倾向于基因退化。

==对人类的傳染病防治==
除了昆虫以外，沃尔巴克氏体还感染各种[[等足目|等足目]]、[[蜘蛛|蜘蛛]]、[[螨|螨]]，许多种[[线虫|线虫]](一大类[[寄生虫|寄生虫]]，包括引起人类的[[蟠尾丝虫症|蟠尾丝虫症]] ("河盲症")、[[象皮病|象皮病]]，引起犬类疾病的[[犬心丝虫|犬心丝虫]]等）。不仅是导致这些疾病的[[丝虫|丝虫]]会被沃尔巴克氏体感染，而且沃尔巴克氏体在这些疾病中扮演了不寻常角色。许多寄生丝虫的致病性源自沃尔克氏体的宿主免疫相应。使用[[多西环素|多西环素]]杀死蟠尾丝虫体内的沃尔巴克氏体，常导致丝虫死亡或不育。<ref name="pmid12684759">{{cite journal |author=Hoerauf A, Mand S, Fischer K, et al. |title=Doxycycline as a novel strategy against bancroftian filariasis-depletion of ''Wolbachia'' endosymbionts from Wuchereria bancrofti and stop of microfilaria production |journal=Med. Microbiol. Immunol. |volume=192 |issue=4 |pages=211–6 |year=2003 |pmid=12684759 |doi=10.1007/s00430-002-0174-6}}</ref>因此，现在对[[蟠尾丝虫症|蟠尾丝虫症]]的临床用药使用抗生素[[多西环素|多西环素]]杀死丝虫体内的内共生的沃尔巴克氏体，代替以[[伊维菌素|伊维菌素]]这种对人体毒副作用更大的抗丝虫药。<ref name="pmid15964448">{{Cite journal |last1=Taylor |first1=MJ |last2=Makunde |first2=WH |last3=McGarry |first3=HF |last4=Turner |first4=JD |last5=Mand |first5=S |last6=Hoerauf |first6=A |title=Macrofilaricidal activity after doxycycline treatment of Wuchereria bancrofti: a double-blind, randomised placebo-controlled trial |journal=Lancet |volume=365 |issue=9477 |pages=2116–21 |year=2005 |pmid=15964448 |doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(05)66591-9}}</ref>

沃尔巴克氏体可用作[[病媒控制|病媒控制]]。如对蚊子群体。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Xi|first=Z|author2=Dean JL |author3=Khoo C |author4=Dobson SL. |title=Generation of a novel Wolbachia infection in Aedes albopictus (Asian tiger mosquito) via embryonic microinjection|journal=Insect Biochem Mol Biol|year=2005|volume=35|issue=8|pages=903–10|pmc=1410910|pmid=15944085|doi=10.1016/j.ibmb.2005.03.015}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last=Moreira|first=LA|author2=Iturbe-ormaetxe I |author3=Jeffery JA |author4=et al. |title=A Wolbachia symbiont in Aedes aegypti limits infection with dengue, Chikungunya, and Plasmodium|journal=Cell|year=2009|volume=139|issue=7|pages=1268–78|pmid=20064373|doi=10.1016/j.cell.2009.11.042}}</ref>这是由于沃尔巴克氏体独特的“细胞质不兼容”特性，这会驱动宿主群体的基因扩散。群体遗传学的计算模型预计，在天然群体中引入沃尔巴克氏体将降低病源传播，降低整体的疾病负担。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Hancock|first=PA|author2=Sinkins SP |author3=Godfray HC. |title=Strategies for introducing Wolbachia to reduce transmission of mosquito-borne diseases|journal=PLoS Negl Trop Dis.|year=2011|volume=5|issue=4|pages=e1024 |pmc=3082501|pmid=21541357|doi=10.1371/journal.pntd.0001024}}</ref>例如，沃尔巴克氏体可以控制[[登革热|登革热]] 与[[疟疾|疟疾]]，这是通过去除更老的包含了更多病源的昆虫，推动幸存者生下更多年轻的昆虫减缓了抵抗演化的选择压力。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Mcmeniman|first=CJ|author2=Lane RV |author3=Cass BN |author4=et al. |title=Stable introduction of a life-shortening Wolbachia infection into the mosquito Aedes aegypti|journal=Science|year=2009|volume=323|issue=5910|pages=141–4|pmid=19119237|doi=10.1126/science.1165326}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title='Bug' could combat dengue fever|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/health/7804326.stm|date=2 January 2009|work=BBC NEWS|publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation|accessdate=2015-06-12|archive-date=2017-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170804053045/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/health/7804326.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>沃尔巴克氏体菌株wAllbB与wMelPop能降低[[埃及伊蚊|埃及伊蚊]]的登革热传播，wMel菌株对[[白纹伊蚊|白纹伊蚊]]<ref>{{cite journal|last=Blagrove|first=MS|author2=Arias-goeta C |author3=Failloux AB |author4=Sinkins SP. |title=Wolbachia strain wMel induces cytoplasmic incompatibility and blocks dengue transmission in ''Aedes albopictus'' |journal=Proc Natl Acad Sci U S A|year=2012|volume=109|issue=1|pages=255–60 |pmc=3252941|pmid=22123944|doi=10.1073/pnas.1112021108}}</ref>与[[埃及伊蚊|埃及伊蚊]]也有类似效果。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Hoffmann|first=AA|author2=Iturbe-Ormaetxe I |author3=Callahan AG |author4=Phillips BL. |title=Stability of the wMel ''Wolbachia'' Infection following invasion into ''Aedes aegypti'' populations |url=https://archive.org/details/pubmed-PMC4161343|journal=PLoS Negl Trop Dis|year=2014|doi=10.1371/journal.pntd.0003115/}}</ref>此外，沃尔巴克氏体的Wmel菌株被证实对限制[[基孔肯雅症|基孔肯雅症]]的病毒在[[埃及伊蚊|埃及伊蚊]]体内复制有效，比较于未被沃尔巴克氏体感染的蚊子，显著降低了[[基孔肯雅症|基孔肯雅症]]感染与传播。类似现象也发现适用[[黄热病|黄热病毒]]。<ref>{{cite journal|last=van den Hurk |first=AF|author2= Hall-Mendelin S |author3= Pyke AT |author4= Frentiu FD. |title=Impact of ''Wolbachia'' on infection with chikungunya and yellow fever viruses in the mosquito vector ''Aedes aegypti'' |journal=PLoS Negl Trop Dis|year=2012|doi=10.1371/journal.pntd.0001892/}}</ref>
 
2014年，[[中山大学|中山大学]]-[[密歇根州立大学|密歇根州立大学]]热带病虫媒控制联合研究中心奚志勇教授团队、[[中国疾病预防控制中心|中国疾病预防控制中心]]、[[广州市疾病预防控制中心|广州市疾病预防控制中心]]合作，从果蝇、伊蚊和库蚊体内提取沃尔巴克氏体并成功将其导入到登革热媒介[[白纹伊蚊|白纹伊蚊]]体内，建立了稳定的携带新型沃尔巴克氏体的蚊株。携带沃尔巴克氏体的雄蚊与非携带沃尔巴克氏体雌蚊交配所产的卵不能发育。通过大量释放携带沃尔巴克氏体的雄蚊，可以使蚊子种群数量降低至不足以引起登革热流行。这种过程被称为种群控制。携带沃尔巴克氏体的雌蚊无论与哪种雄蚊交配，都能生下携带沃尔巴克氏体的子代。随着蚊子一代代地繁殖，若干代后，整个种群都会携带这种共生菌，蚊子世世代代都失去了传播登革病毒的能力。这种过程就是种群替代。项目已通过中国国内权威专家组的生物安全评估，获得了[[中国农业部|中国农业部]]的现场测试许可证。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.southcn.com/china/content/2014-11/07/content_111718105.htm |title=中大再出新成果 “以蚊治蚊”防登革热，2014-11-07 《南方日报》 |access-date=2015-06-12 |archive-date=2019-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190815035043/http://news.southcn.com/china/content/2014-11/07/content_111718105.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>2015年，该项目组在广州市南沙区一个孤立的有居民岛屿上释放了50万只感染了沃尔巴克氏体的雄蚊的试验。<ref>[http://www.fj.xinhuanet.com/news/2015-05/27/c_1115424673.htm  “科学家在广州释放50万只蚊子”《深圳商报》2015-05-27 转引自英国《卫报》] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150614112433/http://www.fj.xinhuanet.com/news/2015-05/27/c_1115424673.htm |date=2015-06-14 }}</ref>

另一项对西尼罗河病毒研究，在来源于[[埃及伊蚊|埃及伊蚊]]细胞的细胞系Aag2感染沃尔巴克氏体后，病毒RNA复制增强了但分泌病毒被显著抑制。还发现感染了wMelPop菌株的蚊子的抗病毒效果：病毒复制被抑制。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Hussain |first=M|author2= Lu G |author3= Torres S |author4=  Edmonds JH. |title=Effect of ''Wolbachia'' on replication of West Nile virus in a mosquito cell line and adult mosquitoes |journal=J Virol|year=2013|doi=10.1128/JVI.01837-12/}}</ref>

但是，用沃尔巴克氏体降低病源传播的研究比较谨慎。最近一项研究发现在[[跗斑库蚊|跗斑库蚊]]体内的wAlbB菌株改进了西尼罗河病毒的生存。 wAlbB抑制了抗病毒Toll免疫路径的REL1活化子。如果把感染了wAlbB菌株的蚊子大规模释放入自然群体，将是第一种很大增强了虫媒人类传染病。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Dodson |first=BL|author2= Grant H |author3= Oluwatobi P. |title=''Wolbachia'' Enhances West Nile Virus (WNV) Infection in the Mosquito ''Culex tarsalis'' |url=https://archive.org/details/pubmed-PMC4091933 |journal=Plos|year=2014|doi=10.1371/journal.pntd.0002965/}}</ref>。但主流学术界认为，需避免过度解读以上研究结果，因为它很有可能是一个实验室条件下人为产生的一个结果(artifact)。因为该研究所用的是一个短暂携带沃尔巴克氏体的蚊子系统，在该系统中，沃尔巴克氏体并没有与蚊子形成稳定的共生，以至于沃尔巴克氏体只能存在当代的体细胞组织（somatic tissue），不能经卵传递到下一代。也就是，在该系统中，沃尔巴克氏体与蚊宿主的相互作用更像一个病原体。而在所有的应用研究中， 沃尔巴克氏体都是与蚊子形成了稳定共生的关系，可从母亲传递给子子代代。而在所有稳定共生的系统中，沃尔巴克氏体从未发现会增加病毒的复制。

有解释热舞内沃尔巴克氏体导致了活性氧类(ROS)相关的{{tsl|Toll (gene family)|Toll族基因}}通路的活化。该通路是活化抗微生物的[[肽|肽]], [[防御素|防御素]], {{tsl|en|cecropin|蛾血素}}所必需的，可以抑制[[登革热|登革热]]传播。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Pan|first=X|author2=Zhou G |author3=Wu J |author4=et al. |title=Wolbachia induces reactive oxygen species (ROS)-dependent activation of the Toll pathway to control dengue virus in the mosquito ''Aedes aegypti'' |journal=Proc Natl Acad Sci U S A|year=2012|volume=109|issue=1|pages=E23–31|pmc=3252928|pmid=22123956|doi=10.1073/pnas.1116932108}}</ref>[[斯氏按蚊|斯氏按蚊]]感染了''w''AlbB菌株的沃尔巴克氏体后，阻碍了[[恶性疟原虫|恶性疟原虫]]的生命周期，有助于控制[[疟疾|疟疾]]传播。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Bian|first=G|author2=Joshi D |author3=Dong Y |author4=et al. |title=Wolbachia invades ''Anopheles stephensi'' populations and induces refractoriness to Plasmodium infection|journal=Science|year=2013|volume=340|issue=6133|pages=748–51|pmid=23661760|doi=10.1126/science.1236192}}</ref>

